exceptions.exn: Expects a disjunctive pattern with 2 branches.

original: intros m l Hinv Hplanar. destruct l as [| [x x'] l0]. - simpl. left. auto. - simpl. intros Hnot_expf Hring. right. unfold cA, Br1, expf in *. destruct (eq_dim_dec zero zero) as [_|Hneq]; [|contradiction]. rewrite eq_dart_dec_refl in *. destruct Hring as [Hnon_empty [Hdll [Hpr0 [Hpr1 [Hpr2 Hpr3]]]]]. split. + intro Hempty. apply Hnon_empty. destruct l0; auto. + split. * eapply double_link_list_Br1; eauto. * split. { eapply pre_ring0_Br1; eauto. } split. { apply pre_ring1_Br1 with (l := cons x x' l0); auto. } split. { eapply pre_ring2_Br1; eauto. } eapply pre_ring3_Br1; eauto.
